{"tid":2492912,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"14歲男童大埔白石角屋苑墮樓昏迷　送院不治","createTime":"2021-04-17T13:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T13:32:48.000Z","uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"83ac9966440ad5a713bac3fe8f09f15da752d182","tid":2492912,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:00:55.000Z","msg":"今日(17日)下午2時49分，警方接獲一名保安員報案，指發現一名年約10多歲男童倒臥在大埔科進路16號一私人屋苑對開，懷疑他從高處墮下。<br />\n救護人員接報到場，立即將昏迷男童送往那打素醫院治理，憎最後被證實死亡。警方於現場有檢獲遺書。經初步調查，相信死者從上址一單位墮下，死因有待驗屍後確定。"},{"pid":"78484c6f44473b619d3c1b9fabeec5b32b33f2a4","tid":2492912,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:03:14.000Z","msg":"未享受過囡囡就此終結一生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e43e4fbc0b29e83f8f54c94958d05c2daaed16","tid":2492912,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:10:11.000Z","msg":"業主molamola<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03cb34cb110cea06591a942427bf8db9479a6ca","tid":2492912,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:32:04.000Z","msg":"hand foot"},{"pid":"fb85bb4ded2cd641353fb08dd09134f8c5292721","tid":2492912,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78484c6f44473b619d3c1b9fabeec5b32b33f2a4","tid":2492912,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:03:14.000Z","msg":"未享受過囡囡就此終結一生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:32:30.000Z","msg":"慘"},{"pid":"34d7e9c54d1148663ba46cda5fc0838e52cd2cc0","tid":2492912,"uid":96728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:32:48.000Z","msg":"咁快變吉宅...rip"}]}